<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山坡上下起暴雨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西他们知道黑雨大王要攻击他们了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山神突然出现。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们快走！” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还能控制这座山，但是黑雨大王太强大，我阻挡不了太久！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你！” 罗西大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西他们离开鸟鸣山很远后，才停下来休息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧向罗西行礼道谢：“你不是这里人，你是从海的另一边来的吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我来自另一个世界。” 罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太神奇了！” 唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我和我的徒弟们要去西天，希望能取得佛祖的真经。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“山神告诉我了。” 罗西说，“我很想帮你，但我要先找到回家的方法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没关系。” 唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还有两个徒弟，只是不知道他们去哪儿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 罗西突然想起了什么，“山神说，孙悟空是你的徒弟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108408</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他现在在我的世界。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我和他打架的时候，被他骗进了传送门，所以我来到了这里。” 她摇了摇头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119814</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他制造了很多麻烦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一点儿都不惊讶。” 唐僧叹了一口气，“悟空还在学习怎么向善。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不惊讶。” 悟净看了看周围，“八戒也不知道去哪儿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西大吃一惊：“我也见到他了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他也在你的世界吗？” 悟净扬了扬眉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，他在监狱。” 罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧双手抱头：“他们为什么学不会向善呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看来我必须快点回家。” 罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不在的时候，不知道孙悟空又制造了什么麻烦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她叹了一口气：“但是回去了我也不知道要怎么办。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180681</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孙悟空和我一样强大……我没法打败他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180681</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，我可以阻止他。” 唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我们打不开传送门，师父。” 悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好像只有悟空和黑雨大王才能打开。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别忘了迅翼。” 唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她现在在跟观音菩萨学习，她一定会帮我们的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父。” 悟净说，“普陀山很远。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上次我留下您一个人，您被黑雨大王抓走了。我不能再离开您了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去吧。” 罗西说，“你告诉我方向就行。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净皱了皱眉：“你不是神仙，可能找不到那里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232011</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西耸了耸肩：“让我试试。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“普陀山在南海中央。” 悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他告诉罗西如何找到那座山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞向南海。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在南海上找了很久，一座山都没有看到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，她看到了另一片大陆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我找遍了整个南海。” 罗西嘀咕着说，“普陀山到底在……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天空中光芒四射，一个声音响起：“你是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>